text: Frunze () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltymanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 163 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Iglino, 6 km from Kaltymanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Frunze, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
